    • Field Detail

      • VERSION

        public static final String VERSION
        The official version assigned when the binaries were built.

      • VERSION_MAVEN

        public static final String VERSION_MAVEN
        The version of the binaries according to Maven. This should always be the same as VERSION, if it is not then the binaries were incorrectly built.

      • BUILD_VERSION

        public static final String BUILD_VERSION
        The version assigned to the build. For release builds this should always be the same as VERSION. Development or snapshot builds will have appended the revision since the last official release and the commitish.

      • BUILD_COMMIT

        public static final String BUILD_COMMIT
        The full commit hash of the source code from which these binaries were built.

      • BUILD_TIMESTAMP

        public static final Date BUILD_TIMESTAMP
        The date and time when these binaries were built.

      • BUILD_REVISION

        public static final int BUILD_REVISION
        The number of revisions since the last official release. For release builds this will always be 0. For snapshot builds, this is the number of commits since the first snapshot for this version. For development builds, this is the number of commits since the last official release.
